 />\n從美國蔓延至台灣、澳大利亚、中國廣東省<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要查，查來自南美我櫃更好啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>其實紅火蟻源至南美<br />\n<br />\n1930年代傳入美國<br />\n<br />\n2001年及2002年透過貨櫃運輸及草皮外銷等途徑<br />\n<br />\n從美國蔓延至台灣、澳大利亚、中國廣東省<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要查，查來自南美我櫃更好啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入面咪有講點解係查中國集裝箱<br />\n同埋d 簡體字改改佢，唔係會比人扣人工"},{"pid":"a8f531c836fee9a50a5f54efff35100532629c11","tid":309543,"uid":7359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:00:12.000Z","msg":"要搵會長出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb6a33e3afd1152ebc01d5fa8ea589906eaf546","tid":309543,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:07:27.000Z","msg":"習總送大禮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf38a6eaf5e51075abc51fcadd42089ba7a13f7b","tid":309543,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:09:07.000Z","msg":"輸出紅火蟻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e62587ec5d16cc339510ec2ed0e6774792b036","tid":309543,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:09:57.000Z","msg":"蟻篇來了"},{"pid":"cfb552317f7537aa8b57821464b8f5307529991e","tid":309543,"uid":10219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:19:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實紅火蟻源至南美<br />\n<br />\n1930年代傳入美國<br />\n<br />\n2001年及2002年透過貨櫃運輸及草皮外銷等途徑<br />\n<br />\n從美國蔓延至台灣、澳大利<span style=\"color: red;\">亚</span>、中國廣東省<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要查，查來自南美我櫃更好啦</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}